   <li><a class='dropdown-item' href='/fr/'>FR Français</a></li>\n                <li><a class='dropdown-item' href='/id/'>ID bahasa Indonesia</a></li>\n                <li><a class='dropdown-item' href='/pt/'>PT Português</a></li>\n                <li><a class='dropdown-item' href='/th/'>TH ภาษาไทย</a></li>\n                <li><a class='dropdown-item' href='/vi/'>VI Tiếng Việt</a></li>\n                -->\n              </ul>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n    \n          <form class=\"d-flex\" role=\"search\" action=\"search\">\n            <input class=\"form-control me-2 ui-autocomplete-input\" type=\"search\" placeholder=\"Search\" aria-label=\"Search\" id=\"navautosearch\" name=\"q\" autocomplete=\"off\">\n          </form>\n    \n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <script> sidebar160(\"leftside_banner\", \"left\"); </script>\n    <script> sidebar160(\"rightside_banner\", \"right\"); </script>\n\n    <div class=\"page\">\n    <div class=\"page-content container\" role=\"main\">\n    <div class=\"text-center\">\n    <a href=\"Vorax_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/UI_S13_LegendStitching_03.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Overrealm_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/UI_S12_LengJing_White01.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Outlaw_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/GamePlay/UI_Item_S11ChipMatching0_Icon.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Sandlord_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Coin/128/UI_Money_S10EquipEnchantMaterial_10_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Arcana_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/128/UI_S9Pet_FateStar_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"The_Frozen_Canvas_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/GamePlay/UI_Item_S8Gameplay_Snow2_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Clockwork_Ballet_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/128/UI_MysticTreeRespecPoint_Icon_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Whispering_Mist_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/GamePlay/UI_S6Gameplay_Tile_bench.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Nightmare_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/GamePlay/UI_Item_S5Gameplay_DreamTreasure_Almighty_C_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Aeterna_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Silhouette/Talent/S4/UI_S4Gameplay_talent01_Icon_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Cube_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/128/UI_S3Gameplay_Beads_Icon_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Blacksail_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/128/UI_S2BossTicket3_Icon_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    <a href=\"Dark_Surge_Season\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Item/128/UI_Item_yimozhihe_Icon_128.webp\" class=\"size48\"></a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"text-center mb-2\"><a href=\"https://l.taptap.cn/SyBkGgT1?channel=rep-rep_voftpwn7cks\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/image/torchlight/p3_20251226_cn.webp\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></a></div>\n    <ul class=\"nav nav-tabs d-flex flex-wrap\" role=\"tablist\"><li class=\"nav-item\" role=\"presentation\"><button class=\"nav-link active\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" data-bs-target=\"#第一章\">第一章 /15 </button></li><li class=\"nav-item\" role=\"presentation\"><button class=\"nav-link\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-bs-target=\"#第一章节-成就之路\" tabindex=\"-1\">第一章节 - 成就之路 /11 </button></li></ul><div class=\"tab-content\"><div id=\"第一章\" class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"card mb-2 \">\n    <div class=\"card-header\">第一章 /15 </div>\n    <div class=\"collapse show\">\n    \n    \n    <div id=\"DataTables_Table_0_wrapper\" class=\"dataTables_wrapper dt-bootstrap5 no-footer\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\"></div><div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\"><div id=\"DataTables_Table_0_filter\" class=\"dataTables_filter\"><label>Search:<input type=\"search\" class=\"form-control form-control-sm\" placeholder=\"\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_0\"></label></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\"><table class=\"table table-hover table-striped DataTable dataTable no-footer\" id=\"DataTables_Table_0\"><thead><tr><th class=\"sorting\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_0\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" aria-label=\"name: activate to sort column ascending\">name</th><th class=\"sorting\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_0\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" aria-label=\"describe: activate to sort column ascending\">describe</th><th class=\"sorting\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_0\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" aria-label=\"Level: activate to sort column ascending\">Level</th><th class=\"sorting\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_0\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" aria-label=\"boss: activate to sort column ascending\">boss</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Hideout_-_Ember%27s_Rest\">避难所-余烬之息</a></td><td>火炬之光的避难所，建立在环绕的灾烬之中，宛若海啸和暴雨之中的一叶孤岛。“灾烬是一切不幸的根源，但也是我们不得不去驯服的东西。”</td><td>2</td><td><a href=\"Agito%27s_Chosen_%C2%B7_Lean\">觉醒者圣子·莱安</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"Ancient_Passage\">远古通道</a></td><td>在密林的遮蔽下，终年飘雨的山地笼罩在深沉的暮色中。诡异的灾烬侵蚀着这里的大地，而这些灾烬的源头，竟然是一座早已废弃的高塔。</td><td>2</td><td><a href=\"Wristblade_Agito\">臂刃觉醒者</a></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Ancient_Battleground\">上古战场</a></td><td>安达岭山地的深处，哥布林们搭建了一个穷困潦倒的村子，在此繁衍生息。留在村落的多是老弱妇孺，三岁小孩也能将它们打的抱头鼠窜。但现在，似乎发生了什么诡异的变化……</td><td>4</td><td><a href=\"Aember_Bastion\">灾烬缓魔</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"Anti-Dragon_Bulwark\">对龙巨墙</a></td><td>分割大地的巨大城墙，曾经是上古英雄直面巨龙之地。</td><td>6</td><td><a href=\"Agito_Punisher\">觉醒惩罚者</a></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Dragonbone_Ridge\">龙骨山脊</a></td><td>终息之战后，无数巨龙陨落于此。千万年过去，它们的身躯化为了这片荒原。</td><td>7</td><td><a href=\"Plateau_Dragonbone_Griffin\">高原龙骨狮鹫</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"Dragonbone_Plains\">龙骨平原</a></td><td>向东穿越龙骨山脊，面前的是一片更为开阔的高原。据说龙骨山脊的最深处，藏着通向矮人地底王国的入口</td><td>9</td><td></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Lost_Mine\">失落矿洞</a></td><td>这处被矮人王国遗忘已久的远古矿洞，突兀地响起了机械运行的轰鸣声。</td><td>10</td><td><a href=\"Trog_Boss\">地魔首领</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"King%27s_Pass\">国王甬道</a></td><td>搭乘破旧的升降机向更深处前进，机械的轰鸣声愈发清晰。当心那些还在运作的采矿装置，还有蜂拥而至的矮人。</td><td>11</td><td><a href=\"Dwarven_Automaton\">矮人机甲</a></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Heart_of_Kazsan\">卡兹萨恩之心</a></td><td>矮人矿洞的最深处，相传是矮人王的实验室。巨大的充电桩上盘踞着虎视眈眈的机械守卫，他们冰冷而无情地恪守着国王的指令——入侵者，无可赦。</td><td>13</td><td><a href=\"Dwarf_King\">矮人王</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"Deserted_Road\">荒芜山道</a></td><td>先前并没有灾烬痕迹的龙骨平原，因为神秘觉醒者的到来，已经被灾烬彻底污染了。</td><td>14</td><td><a href=\"Abyssal_Agito\">深渊觉醒者</a></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Manella\">马内拉雨林</a></td><td>乘坐船只横跨锡尼河，便来到了绿意盎然的马内拉雨林。别被这些生机勃勃的表象迷惑，这里的蛊虫可不是吃素的。</td><td>15</td><td><a href=\"Great_Worm\">巨型蠕虫</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"Riverside\">溪地虫谷</a></td><td>穿越蜿蜒崎岖的丛林小径，在圣泉中沐浴，便来到了林中夫人的长居之处。她美丽而圣洁，优雅而高贵。她是所有虫子们共同的母亲。</td><td>16</td><td><a href=\"Eroded_Wing_Butterfly\">蚀翼之蝶</a></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Verdant_Land\">阴翳之地</a></td><td>赛迦族留下的古遗迹。吟游诗人曾在这里驻足，为她写下诗篇。“无名的英雄沉睡森林，逝去的身躯依然屹立。”</td><td>19</td><td><a href=\"Mutated_Liv\">异化丽芙</a></td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td><a href=\"Treasure_Trove%3A_New_Ear_Hills\">藏宝地：新穗山丘</a></td><td>庞大的赫尔曼帝国瓦解后，在莱提斯大陆上留下许多藏宝地。这些藏宝地承载着帝国时代的辉煌和荣耀，也隐藏着未知的危险和宝藏。</td><td>7</td><td></td></tr><tr class=\"odd\"><td><a href=\"Treasure_Trove%3A_Nectar_Valley\">藏宝地：蜜露溪谷</a></td><td>庞大的赫尔曼帝国瓦解后，在莱提斯大陆上留下许多藏宝地。这些藏宝地承载着帝国时代的辉煌和荣耀，也隐藏着未知的危险和宝藏。</td><td>16</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-5\"></div><div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-7\"></div></div></div>\n    \n    </div>\n</div></div><div id=\"第一章节-成就之路\" class=\"tab-pane fade\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div class=\"card mb-2 \">\n    <div class=\"card-header\">第一章节 - 成就之路 /11 </div>\n    <div class=\"collapse show\">\n    \n    \n    <div id=\"DataTables_Table_1_wrapper\" class=\"dataTables_wrapper dt-bootstrap5 no-footer\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\"></div><div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\"><div id=\"DataTables_Table_1_filter\" class=\"dataTables_filter\"><label>Search:<input type=\"search\" class=\"form-control form-control-sm\" placeholder=\"\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_1\"></label></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\"><table class=\"table table-hover table-striped DataTable dataTable no-footer\" id=\"DataTables_Table_1\"><thead><tr><th class=\"sorting\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" aria-label=\"title: activate to sort column ascending\">title</th><th class=\"sorting\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"DataTables_Table_1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" aria-label=\"desc: activate to sort column ascending\">desc</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<tr class=\"odd\"><td>灾厄之火（狂人）</td><td><li>使用英雄狂人完成第一章节</li><br>奖励: <a data-hover=\"/cache/cn/Torchlight_Money_hover/c00c743849d975e49b24541f73080f49f1f5bbe4231ed6d3f6c1fd93a43346de\" href=\"Jagged_Primocryst\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI/Textures/Common/Icon/Coin/128/UI_Money_BreakCrystal_Icon_128.webp\" height=\"24\" loading=\"lazy\">碎裂原晶</a> x10</td></tr><tr class=\"even\"><td>灾厄之火（圣枪）</td><td><li>使用英雄圣枪完成第一章节</li><br>奖励: <a data-hover=\"/cache/cn/Torchlight_Money_hover/c00c743849d975e49b24541f73080f49f1f5bbe4231ed6d3f6c1fd93a43346de\" href=\"Jagged_Primocryst\"><img src=\"https://cdn.tlidb.com/UI